# Watchlist data — DO NOT COMMIT while repo is public.
# These files contain Midya's client roster + consortium peers and must stay
# private. When the repo is flipped to private (or watchlist is injected via
# GitHub Actions secrets), remove these lines and commit the files normally.
# See docs/superpowers/specs/2026-05-21-client-aware-briefing-design.md
config/watchlist.yaml
